title: Winnie, Cat Pirate
description: Give a player $5 to purchase Winnie on top of your bid.

title: Mystery Box
description: Each player may spend $5 to do an extra Makeover or Sabotage.

title: Walk A Mile In Her Paws
description:
Everyone must interacting with the board as if their hands were paws until end of round.
First person to stop loses $5.

title: Mondays
description: Select a player. They must approach a person outside the game and proudly proclaim “I Hate Mondays”, or lose $5.

title: Prisoner's Dilemma
description: Everyone makes a vote, thumbs up for Greed and thumbs down for Heed. If Greed has majority, everyone who voted Greed loses 10 money. If Heed gets majority, everyone who voted Greed gains 10 money.

title: Marked Up Prices

description: Everyone returns selects a cat and donates it to the player on their left.

description: Until the end of round, reverse all cat scores.

title: Marked Down Prices
description: Add an extra Action card to in play. Reduce costs of all actions by 2$.
